Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不巧 剛好都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船是Justice和Freedom的專用支援艦
