Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是Coordinator 笨蛋還是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法
